            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~symbolset" class="author" title="author name and user ID">symbolset (646467) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3596513&cid=43317167">(#43317167)</a></h4>
