            <h4 class="avatar-tiny"><a href="//beta.slashdot.org/~DanielRavenNest" class="author" title="author name and user ID">DanielRavenNest (107550) </a> | about a year ago | <a href="//beta.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3596513&cid=43320753">(#43320753)</a></h4>
